snippet.title: Kylie Jenner: Grinch Cupcakes with Stormi
snippet.description:
In celebration of my KYLIE X GRINCH collection launching today, Stormi and I made Grinch cupcakes! 

Shop my limited edition Grinch holiday collection at http://kyliecosmetics.com today at 3pm PST
